OL,5, Nearly 1.5 million customers have been 
OL,6, affected by energy firms collapsing    
OL,7, under soaring gas prices.              
OL,9,FAvro Energy and Green ceased trading on
OL,10,FWednesday and their 830,000 combined   
OL,11,Fcustomers face being switched to a new,
OL,12,Fpotentially more expensive, provider.  
OL,14,FAll affected customers will still      
OL,15,Freceive energy while a new supplier is 
OL,16,Fappointed by watchdog Ofgem.           
OL,18,FNeil Lawrence, director of retail at   
OL,19,FOfgem, said its "number one priority is
OL,20,Fto protect customers."                 
